Introduction

AIMERS is a group under HYPER RHYTHM that debuted on November 17, 2022. The group consists of 6 members: Seunghyun, Eunjun, Doryun, Yoel, Seunghwan, and Wooyoung.

They debuted with their mini album, "STAGE 0. BETTING STARTS".
